snippet.title: Triple Bubble: Triple mode
snippet.description:
This video shows the Triple mode, where you can shoot bubbles from 3 launchers to cover a wider playfield. The demo has been released, so you can play it now!

🌏 Vircon32 website: https://www.vircon32.com
